sentences: He rose to fame in 2018 with a remix of Virtual Self's "Particle Arts" uploaded onto his SoundCloud account.
A digital download release of his song was issued on 2 February 2018.
On 9 February 2018 he released a remix of "Particle Arts" by Virtual Self.
On 2 March 2018, a remix of Daft Punk's "Rinzler" (from Tron: Legacy) was released, and premiered on Dancing Astronaut.
On 30 March 2018, a remix of "Radioactivity" by Kraftwerk was released on all platforms.

His debut extended play, Sentience, which comprises four tracks was released on August 24, 2018 through Zeds Dead' label, Deadbeats.1788-L performed his first live show on July, 2018 in Los Angeles, California.
